The Multimodal Interaction Working Group has published a Working Draft of Discovery &#38; Registration of Multimodal Modality Components: State Handling. This document is addressed to people who want either to develop Modality Components for Multimodal Applications distributed over a local network or &#8220;in the cloud&#8221;. With this goal, in a multimodal system implemented according to [&#8230;]<img src="https://www.w3.org/analytics/piwik/piwik.php?idsite=7&amp;rec=1&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2Fblog%2Fnews%2Farchives%2F4756%3Fpk_campaign%3Dfeed%26pk_kwd%3Ddiscovery-registration-of-multimodal-modality-components-state-handling-draft-published&amp;action_name=Discovery+and+Registration+of+Multimodal+Modality+Components%3A+State+Handling+Draft+Published&amp;urlref=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2Fblog%2Fnews%2Ffeed" style="border:0;width:0;height:0" width="0" height="0" alt="" />
