<content:encoded>
<![CDATA[
<p>The <a href="http://www.w3.org/2008/webapps/">Web Applications Working Group</a> invites implementation of the Candidate Recommendation of <a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/2015/CR-webstorage-20150609/">Web Storage (Second Edition)</a>. This specification defines an API for persistent data storage of key-value pair data in Web clients, and introduces two related mechanisms, similar to HTTP session cookies, for storing name-value pairs on the client side. Learn more about the <a href="http://www.w3.org/2006/rwc/">Rich Web Client Activity</a>.</p> <p><img src="https://www.w3.org/analytics/piwik/piwik.php?idsite=7&amp;rec=1&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2Fblog%2Fnews%2Farchives%2F4751%3Fpk_campaign%3Dfeed%26pk_kwd%3Dw3c-invites-implementations-of-web-storage-second-edition&amp;action_name=W3C+Invites+Implementations+of+Web+Storage+%28Second+Edition%29&amp;urlref=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2Fblog%2Fnews%2Ffeed" style="border:0;width:0;height:0" width="0" height="0" alt="" /></p>
